title: Sex Pistols : Anarchy In The USA Bootleg
description:
Obscure boot CD originating from god knows what country.
Occasionally seen on ebay in LP & CD form.

A mixture of demos & stuff from NMTB & GRNRS, and also some
live tracks.

Not for the hardcore Pistols fan, but a good intro for
those, who perhaps, are just interested.
